Refund Policy

If you’ve purchased the app and are not happy with it, you are eligible for a full reimbursement within 30 days of your purchase.

To obtain your refund, please send your order ID or forward the original email receipt from your purchase. This will help speed up the process, and make sure that your refund is issued within 48 hours.

If you have any additional questions or would like to request a refund, feel free to contact me personally. @ tristan.edwards@me.com